data.description: Check out this great 2,499 sq. ft. 4 bedroom/3 bath home in the Riviera Estates community in Palm Coast.  The home sits on a corner and has a beautiful view of the pond with a fountain.  As you enter the home you'll see a large dining area on the right and a fabulous water view from the living room through the triple sliding doors in the center with 2 sets of double sliders on either side.  The primary bedroom has a  walk-in closet, garden tub with separate shower and two separate vanities. The kitchen has granite countertops, 42'' cabinets with plenty of drawers, stainless appliances, a long breakfast bar and a breakfast area overlooking the pond.  This corner lot has plenty of privacy and the backyard is curved so the pond surrounds 2 sides of the yard.  Roof was replaced in 2021.  Call now for a showing now.
